# Functional document maintenance

**Canonical path:** `d:\Project\Web\docs\FUNCTIONAL.md`

Edit the functional spec in the **Web** repo (`d:\Project\Web\docs\`), not in `Android/docs/`.

When changing mobile behaviour, update `d:\Project\Web\docs\FUNCTIONAL.md` in the same session (sections + §13 Changelog + Last updated date).

See `d:\Project\Web\.cursor\rules\functional-doc.mdc` for full rules.
